Class ProgramVisualization

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.VisualizationObject
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.ProgramVisualization
public class ProgramVisualization
extends VisualizationObject
ProgramVisualization is a class that compiles data and organizes it in a easily readable manner using a series of methods to create different aspects of the visualization
